{"event_id": "evt_20260211_170500_ads_fix", "ts": "2026-02-11T17:05:00.000000+00:00", "agent": "CLAUDE", "role": "Frontend_Engineer", "action_type": "bug_fix", "description": "Fixed corrupt ADS event (line 203): replaced UTF-8 em-dash with ASCII dashes. Em-dash in seek-backward path caused logger.py _get_last_event() to crash (UnicodeDecodeError at byte 0x94 mid-sequence). This broke DTTP /request endpoint (500), which broke PreToolUse hook (HTML instead of JSON), which fail-closed ALL Write/Edit ops. Filed REQ-006 to Backend_Engineer for root cause fix in logger.py.", "spec_ref": "SPEC-021", "authorized": true, "prev_hash": "3680505229d7aeebfb0e26211854334fd956caa9019e3e3b9fd9d9817850c218", "hash": "bba7687fc8f5eabd814993571ceb8c7cf79eb6f134841f90f14435fa3a1b76f8"}
